HEADWORD: Saltmouth
<hw>Salt"mouth`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A wide-mouthed
bottle with glass stopper for holding chemicals, especially crystallized
salts.</def>⟦br⟧
